org.batfish.coordinator.id

Class FileBasedIdManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.identifiers.FileBasedIdResolver
      • org.batfish.coordinator.id.FileBasedIdManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IdManager, IdResolver

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public class FileBasedIdManager
extends FileBasedIdResolver
implements IdManager
    Filesystem based IdManager capable of writing mappings used by FileBasedIdResolver, from which it inherits. Intended to be used together with FileBasedStorage.
